HEADWORD: Wrongful
<hw>Wrong"ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Full of wrong;
injurious; unjust; unfair; <as>as, a <ex>wrongful</ex> taking of
property; <ex>wrongful</ex> dealing.</as></def> --
<wordforms><wf>Wrong"ful*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Wrong"ful*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

